

== Running the test suite ==

 * Unit Tests
   To run the unit tests just use the command: nosetests tests/unit/*.py
 
 * Functional tests
   To be able do run functional tests you will need to start mongrel2. There is a ready configuration inside
   tests/m2env. To start mongrel2 just run: tests/startm2.sh and then you will be able ro tuns the tests.
